What up?! 

It’s been a while since I’ve posted to my feed. While stories are easy, posting to my feed has become harder for me lately. It’s not because I don’t have content, it’s just that it doesn’t feed my soul the way it used to. Plus, there’s always the fear of IG taking down my space on there platform. All that effort put into building something that could disappear in a second!

Instead, I’ve been focusing on what truly makes me happy: creating. That’s my passion, and it’s where my energy goes. But I do look forward to the day when I feel that insistent need to post again. When that day comes, I’ll share what I’ve been working on and hopefully make you think, smile, feel, and take in the energy I’m bringing.

I want to take a moment to thank my OG followers and all the new ones for continuing to support me. You guys are amazing!

🎶🚀 **Four Years of Musical Journeys: A Look Back & Ahead** 🚀🎶

🌟 **Four years ago today**, I embarked on a solo voyage with my first project under my very own imprint. It was the starting note of an incredible symphony that's been my life in music.

✨ **The Breakthrough:** Not long after, I inked a deal with a jazz label, stepping into the spotlight to share not just my beats but also to elevate fellow creators, releasing multiple projects that echoed our collective passion.

🔥 **Going Solo:** The end of that deal wasn't a finale but an overture to greater independence. I became my own distributor, cutting out the middleman and delivering my music straight from my soul to the world's ears.

💡 **New Horizons:** As my own distributor, I've dropped singles that are pieces of my heart set to rhythm. But the most thrilling? Reuniting with the mentor who first guided me to the melody of life. Together, we're now a duo, crafting a 13-track labor of love set to debut next year.

🌈 **Reflecting & Dreaming:** These four years have been an odyssey, a tapestry of trials, triumphs, and tunes. I've grown, I've learned, and I've been inspired by every note along the way.

🔮 **Looking Forward:** As the calendar turns, I'm buzzing with excitement for what 2024 holds. More beats, more soul, and more journeys await.

🙏 **Thank You:** To everyone who's been part of this ride, your support is my rhythm. Let's keep the music playing. Here's to the next chapter! 🥂
